OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA dry day with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunny spells. Light to moderate
OL,7,Feasterly winds. Becoming cloudy
OL,8,Fthrough the evening and overnight,
OL,9,Fwith hill fog and a chance of drizzle.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FEarly
OL,12,Fcloud and mist clearing Thursday and
OL,13,FFriday to give long sunny spells.
OL,14,FBreezy Thursday, easing Friday.
OL,15,FCloudier Saturday, but with sunny
OL,16,Fintervals and a risk of showers.
OL,17,FTemperatures increasing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
